    "description": "一个面向电商订单履约的中等复杂工作流，处理从订单创建到发货的全链路流程，包含库存预占、支付、物流、异常处理与审计日志。",
    "scene": "generic",
    "inputs": [
      {
        "name": "order_event",
        "label": "前端订单创建事件数据",
        "type": "text",
        "required": true
      }
    ],
    "output_contract": {
      "final_order_status": "string",
      "fulfillment_result": "string (success/partial_success/failure)",
      "payment_transaction_id": "string (optional)",
      "logistics_order_id": "string (optional)",
      "audit_log_id": "string",
      "error_messages": "array (optional)"
    },
    "steps": [
      {
        "id": "start_1",
        "type": "start",
        "config": {
          "input_mapping": {
            "order_event": "{{inputs.order_event}}"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "parse_order",
        "type": "code",
        "config": {
          "language": "python",
          "script": "import json\norder_data = json.loads(order_event)\nreturn {\n    'order_id': order_data.get('order_id'),\n    'user_id': order_data.get('user_id'),\n    'items': order_data.get('items', []),\n    'total_amount': order_data.get('total_amount'),\n    'shipping_address': order_data.get('shipping_address')\n}",
          "example_key": "parse_json",
          "variables": {
            "order_event": "{{steps.start_1.output.order_event}}"
          },
          "error_strategy": "fail-branch"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "inventory_lock",
        "type": "tool",
        "config": {
          "method": "post",
          "url": "http://example.com/api/inventory/lock",
          "headers": {
            "Content-Type": "application/json"
          },
          "body": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}",
            "items": "{{steps.parse_order.output.items}}"
          },
          "variables": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}",
            "items": "{{steps.parse_order.output.items}}"
          },
          "error_strategy": "fail-branch"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "payment_process",
        "type": "tool",
        "config": {
          "method": "post",
          "url": "http://example.com/api/payment/charge",
          "headers": {
            "Content-Type": "application/json"
          },
          "body": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}",
            "amount": "{{steps.parse_order.output.total_amount}}",
            "user_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.user_id}}"
          },
          "variables": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}",
            "amount": "{{steps.parse_order.output.total_amount}}",
            "user_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.user_id}}"
          },
          "error_strategy": "fail-branch"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "logistics_create",
        "type": "tool",
        "config": {
          "method": "post",
          "url": "http://example.com/api/logistics/create",
          "headers": {
            "Content-Type": "application/json"
          },
          "body": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}",
            "address": "{{steps.parse_order.output.shipping_address}}",
            "items": "{{steps.parse_order.output.items}}"
          },
          "variables": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}",
            "address": "{{steps.parse_order.output.shipping_address}}",
            "items": "{{steps.parse_order.output.items}}"
          },
          "error_strategy": "fail-branch"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "check_payment_success",
        "type": "ifelse",
        "config": {
          "condition": "{{steps.payment_process.output.status}} == 'success'",
          "cases": [
            {
              "id": "success",
              "condition": "{{steps.payment_process.output.status}} == 'success'"
            },
            {
              "id": "failure",
              "condition": "{{steps.payment_process.output.status}} != 'success'"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "payment_failure_handler",
        "type": "tool",
        "config": {
          "method": "post",
          "url": "http://example.com/api/notification/send",
          "headers": {
            "Content-Type": "application/json"
          },
          "body": {
            "type": "payment_failure",
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}",
            "user_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.user_id}}",
            "amount": "{{steps.parse_order.output.total_amount}}",
            "channels": [
              "dingtalk",
              "sms"
            ]
          },
          "variables": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}",
            "user_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.user_id}}",
            "amount": "{{steps.parse_order.output.total_amount}}"
          },
          "error_strategy": "fail-branch"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "inventory_release",
        "type": "tool",
        "config": {
          "method": "post",
          "url": "http://example.com/api/inventory/release",
          "headers": {
            "Content-Type": "application/json"
          },
          "body": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}",
            "reason": "payment_failed"
          },
          "variables": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "aggregate_success",
        "type": "variable_aggregator",
        "config": {
          "variables": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}",
            "payment_tx_id": "{{steps.payment_process.output.transaction_id}}",
            "logistics_id": "{{steps.logistics_create.output.logistics_order_id}}",
            "inventory_status": "{{steps.inventory_lock.output.status}}"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "aggregate_failure",
        "type": "variable_aggregator",
        "config": {
          "variables": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}",
            "error_reason": "Payment failed",
            "inventory_released": true
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "audit_log",
        "type": "tool",
        "config": {
          "method": "post",
          "url": "http://example.com/api/audit/log",
          "headers": {
            "Content-Type": "application/json"
          },
          "body": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}",
            "action": "order_fulfillment",
            "status": "{{steps.aggregate_success.output.payment_tx_id ? 'success' : 'failure'}}",
            "details": "{{steps.aggregate_success.output || steps.aggregate_failure.output}}"
          },
          "variables": {
            "order_id": "{{steps.parse_order.output.order_id}}"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "format_result",
        "type": "code",
        "config": {
          "language": "python",
          "script": "audit_output = audit_log_output\nif 'payment_tx_id' in aggregate_success_output:\n    return {\n        'final_order_status': 'fulfilled',\n        'fulfillment_result': 'success',\n        'payment_transaction_id': aggregate_success_output.get('payment_tx_id'),\n        'logistics_order_id': aggregate_success_output.get('logistics_id'),\n        'audit_log_id': audit_output.get('log_id'),\n        'error_messages': []\n    }\nelse:\n    return {\n        'final_order_status': 'cancelled',\n        'fulfillment_result': 'failure',\n        'payment_transaction_id': None,\n        'logistics_order_id': None,\n        'audit_log_id': audit_output.get('log_id'),\n        'error_messages': ['Payment processing failed']\n    }",
          "example_key": "format_markdown",
          "variables": {
            "aggregate_success_output": "{{steps.aggregate_success.output}}",
            "aggregate_failure_output": "{{steps.aggregate_failure.output}}",
            "audit_log_output": "{{steps.audit_log.output}}"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "answer_1",
        "type": "answer",
        "config": {
